reporter_caption.center: ANDERSON PROVISIONS, INC. v. OSSWALD, 148 So.2d 572 (Fla.App. 2 Dist. 1963)

caption.center: ANDERSON PROVISIONS, INC., A FLORIDA CORPORATION, APPELLANT, v. JOSEPH

court.center: District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District.

opinion.opinion_text:
The attorneys for Appellee have filed a Motion to Dismiss the Appeal in this cause, and upon consideration, it is
Ordered that the said Motion be and the same is hereby granted and the Appeal in this cause commenced by Notice of Appeal filed in the Court of Record for Broward County, Florida, on December 3, 1962, be and the same is hereby dismissed.
